Sheyala is a shapeshifter and does this with ease.  It takes no energy as she has worked with the magic for years.  But, using the powers of the forms she takes drains her considerably depending on what she becomes.<br>
<br>
Sheyala is not an immortal BUT she dies when she chooses to rest, or when she over exherts her magic(see the adept magic) As to the war on the MO board she is mortal. [she vowed one final war ~_^ I plan for sheyala to die on the MO so whomever wishes to be her end in a fair fight IM me(AIM sephykin14) or email me @ randyjerilacey@peoplepc.com thanks!]<br>
<br>
Shey can call the elements, mindspeak, enchant weapons, and heal but these also drain her.<br>
<br>
ADEPT LEVEL-<br>
Sheyala as written above has one power that drains her so much, that it causes her to die--but now without a good effect.  She has the power to summon the great creature the phoenix and she BECOMES it for a time.  But, once reverting back to form, she dies as the phoenix is burned in flame then reborn anew. And so is Sheya's burden. to carry a growing child that feeds upon it's mother when it is born... <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#993300>- </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite>Amazons Unite</a><font color=#993300> - </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm33>Character Descriptions</a> <font color=#993300> - </font><a href="http://pub163.ezboard.com/bmythicalodysseyforum">Home</a><font color=#993300> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.245c<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

